QuestData.Title: The Skies of Highmountain
QuestData.Description: When you are ready, join me at the base of Thunder Totem.$b$bI would be honored to have you at my side as my tribe once again swears its allegiance to the young Mayla.$b$bTogether, we are Highmountain!
QuestData.LogDescription: Speak with Lasan Skyhorn at the base of Thunder Totem.
QuestData.RewardText: The Skyhorn are with us? This day just got much better.

Objectives.Objective: Wait for Lasan to finish his ritual
